theorem ex1 (a b c : Nat) (h₁ : a = b) (h₂ : b = c) : a + b = 0 + c + b :=
  calc  a + b  = b + b     := by rw [h₁]
        _      = 0 + c + b := rfl
theorem ex4 (p : Nat → Prop) (a b : Nat) (h₁ : p a) (h₂ : p b) : p c :=
  calc  p a := h₁
        _   := h₂
